            <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 32px;">Say Namaste to healthy wholesome nutrients that are essential in order to live a healthy lifestyle!</p>
            <br />
            <p style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif; font-size: 32px;">The ingredients used to prepare our vibrant range of snacks are of superior quality that matches with the highest nutritional standards.
            This implies that there's no wage of artifcial ingredients but only fresh and nutritious ingredients that ensures both good health and good taste.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container has-text-centered">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-size: 40px; font-weight: bold;">Three reasons to go Calo</h2>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="container">
        <div class="columns is-centered">

          <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <figure class="image is-4by3">
                  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dg7wliucz/image/upload/v1515995218/IMG_5788_pnzssf.jpg" alt="Placeholder image">
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="media-content">
                  <p class="title is-4">It's Convenient</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                  <p style="font-size: 20px;">We ship your favourite Calo Snacks right to your door. Free shipping on orders over Rs. 450!</p>
                  <br>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <figure class="image is-4by3">
                  <img src="http://www.thetruthaboutcars.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/Calendar-610x390.jpg" alt="Placeholder image">
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="media-content">
                  <p class="title is-4">It's Flexible</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                  <p style="font-size: 20px;">Deliveries arrive on your schedule. Pause, skip, or cancel anytime with just a few clicks. Enjoy next levels yoga flexbility!</p>
                  <br>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="column is-one-third">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-image">
                <figure class="image is-4by3">
                  <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dg7wliucz/image/upload/v1515738349/logo/calo_club.png" alt="Placeholder image">
                </figure>
              </div>
              <div class="card-content">
                <div class="media-content">
                  <p class="title is-4">It's Low Risk, High Reward</p>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                  <p style="font-size: 20px;">Once you sign up, even if you dont buy anything, you're a member of our <a>Calo Club</a> for free! No hassle, plus you get free stuff!</p>
                  <br>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

